Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:33.86,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,540)}Ruins of Laboratory #1 and #2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:33.86,Main,Chopper+Brook+Franky,0,0,0,,Oh!  Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.46,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I got all this stuff sticking outta me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's a furball!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.25,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That's Guard Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.64,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Just by visualizing them,\Nyou can freely transform between six different forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.34,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This body ain't very stable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:42.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It takes practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:46.02,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey!  Don't play on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:52.65,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What did you say?!  The samurai left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Dammit!  I thought that it's been too quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.70,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Just a short while ago, I told him about a fellow I met who's nothing but a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.93,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,He wanted to know where I had met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.40,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,and I told him that we parted ways near the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:08.61,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Then he ran out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.91,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I was distracted by Nami-san's glorious body\Nso I let my guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:15.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Even though it's inconvenient for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:21.28,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The one who took him outside\Nwhen he was just a head who couldn't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.46,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.66,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It might have been uncalled for, but it was what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:32.23,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,If he gets killed now, it'll be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.64,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:39.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Even though he's a samurai, he doesn't have a torso to hold a sword so all he can do is run away from battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we go and do what we must?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.22,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,That goddamn asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.67,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Luffy!  I'm gonna head out for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.88,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.51,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll show you the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.34,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,so may I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Oh, right!  We need a camera for an opportunity like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.88,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.93,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Zoro, you're going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.64,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.93,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,If Zoro is there,\NSanji-kun will be in fight-mode at all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:21.25,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why do I need to search for that farting samurai just because you're an idiot?!  You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No one wants you here, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.78,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm stuck with a dumbass\Nwho I can't even share this happiness with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:32.78,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was mercilessly struck.\NDo you think my bones were broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:36.52,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No, all that's broken is my dream to see those panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.02,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.12,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:42.62,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So, what should we do about your bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.18,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The most important thing to do now\Nis get our bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.47,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I don't want to be this pervert for another millisecond!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.31,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill me with praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.69,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Please don't make that face with Chopper's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.23,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:02.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The real problem is those damn kids. They're a real pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:07.72,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Franky, I'd appreciate it\Nif you didn't speak with that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.63,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:11.37,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.48,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.67,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Raccoon Dog-chan, how does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.50,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We'll know in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:27.25,Thoughts,Chopper,0,0,0,,Huh!  That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.61,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,What happened?  Sind?  Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.09,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:42.15,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:45.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Chopper.  He says it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.04,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.51,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.95,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's happening to all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.13,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Doran, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.13,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,All the big kids are collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:03.54,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Chopper, what is it?  Are the kids really sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.56,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:09.10,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sind, is there anything that you want right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.57,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What do you usually do at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.40,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Usually?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:20.65,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,After the examination... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.34,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.90,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Then they give us candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:28.76,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.51,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.49,Main,Kid2,0,0,0,,Everyone loves the candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.79,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,It's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.06,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,It's all fizzy and smoke comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.92,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,That's right... We eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.72,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,And when you eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.93,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,you get this happy feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.94,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,It might make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:02.31,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Brownbeard, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.10,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What do you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:08.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,These kids aren't sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:15.67,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?  I patrol outside,\Nso I don't know what goes on in the laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.68,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,but those kids have a serious disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.99,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hang in there, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.35,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Even the little ones look like they're starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:29.49,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,The ever-compassionate Master\Nwent out of his way to gather those kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.28,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,and he's been donating his medical knowledge\Nto treat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.38,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,He's a tenderhearted scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.65,Main,Ally,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.74,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.51,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Look, there's your proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:47.29,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,After missing a single day of treatment,\Nthose kids have already started to collapse from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.37,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.94,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Chopper, what have you learned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:56.58,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,NHC-10.  That's what I found in the kids' bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:00.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There were only faint traces, but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.10,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,a narcotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,A narcotic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:12.27,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Throughout the world, only a few scientists in select countries are allowed to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I know about it because Doctorine used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.39,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There are some legitimate uses for the drug,\Nbut only in the smallest amounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:23.14,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's extremely addictive if you take too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:30.38,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The children have been taking the drug every day for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.56,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They've become chronically addicted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:38.32,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Their bodies crave the next dose in order to stop the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Why?!  Why would they have this in their system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:48.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's so that they can't run away from the lab, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:54.61,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What is this "god of salvation" of yours really doing to these kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.18,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,If you speak ill of Master, you'll pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Chopper, what do we do?\NThey're all collapsing, one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:05.29,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Candy!  Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:09.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You need candy?\NShould I go get some from the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.23,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.70,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They must never eat the candy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:18.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They've been using it to give the drug to the children\Nwithout them knowing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.26,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Strawhat man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.36,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,You'll bring me the candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:29.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I can't.  If Chopper says you can't have it,\Nthen you can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:32.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's our doctor.  Trust him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.10,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:38.72,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Why?  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.97,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Sind, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.58,Main,Kid2,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:51.20,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,You {\i1}said{\i0} that you'd bring me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:10:02.43,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't you!?  Didn't you say that you'd bring me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.93,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.88,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.78,Main,Kid2,0,0,0,,I've never seen Sind like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.05,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:23.70,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Giants are pretty strong, I guess their children are too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.77,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.82,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Why won't you give me the candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.15,Main,Ally,0,0,0,,Sind's not a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:35.81,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,We were all normal size when we came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.67,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,I thought the disease was making us get bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:41.06,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Nothing else is wrong with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:46.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There's no disease\Nthat makes normal humans grow into giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Giants are always giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:53.74,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,The longer a kid has been here, the bigger they become.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.20,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:02.54,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,their pituitary glands have started producing an abnormal amount of growth hormone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.73,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.17,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,These kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.68,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,are being experimented on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.29,Main,Ally,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Hold yourself together, Ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.52,Main,Ally,0,0,0,,I want candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:27.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What was this "Master" thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:31.43,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,using narcotics on such young kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.52,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.39,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The other kids are starting to go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:42.40,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,Candy!  Candy!  Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.45,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.77,Main,Usopp+Franky,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.83,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sind!  Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.08,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Should I fight 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.04,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,No!  Outta the way, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Usopp!  Don't hurt them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Idiot!  Of course I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:23.64,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I knew that they must have been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.90,Flashbacks,Nami,0,0,0,,Let us out of here!{cp583}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.65,Flashbacks,Nami,0,0,0,,I wanna see Mommy and Daddy!{cp583}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:43.73,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's tragic.  They don't even know that they've been manipulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:47.19,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They want to go home!\NThey want to be with their parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.94,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,We have to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:53.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy, I want to save them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:57.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess we'll take 'em all home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:01.53,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Stupid, it's not that easy.\NThere's a mountain of problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:06.14,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,That's right.  Besides, this is all just our interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.75,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Unless we ask the ringleader directly, we won't know any of this for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Isn't it that Master guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:17.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But Zoro, Sanji, and Brook\Nwent to go look for that samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:21.13,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Uh... Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:25.25,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right!  Let's go back to the laboratory...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,to find Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I should stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:34.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I can never forgive Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.38,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,and I want to kick his ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:41.14,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,but I'm worried about the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.22,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I have to look after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.35,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Ye-Yeah!  That's right!  I'll also have to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.31,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey Nami!  That's a dirty trick!  You're just scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:52.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But it'll be pretty bad if the kids get violent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.60,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We'll tie the big ones up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.43,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I don't like it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:04.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,There's no helping it.\NThey're heavyweights when they get violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.32,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And we don't know when they'll wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.94,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,So, who's going to go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:16.09,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The four of us have to get together and meet Trafalgar,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.77,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,or we won't get our bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But it's fine the way it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is definitely not fine!  Take it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:39.36,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The heart of Smoker, Vice Admiral of Navy Unit G-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.49,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,What a thoughtful present, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.45,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,There's no doubt who won that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:15:02.16,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,They'll want to report what happened, and since\Nthey lost their ship they'll come to take one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.06,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Of course, I've already made arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.27,Main,Law,0,0,0,,What about Straw-Hatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.14,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,He's not a problem either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:16.02,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,His crew is being dealt with,\Nand the children will be brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:23.49,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Well, the kids will eventually want to come back\Neven if they're left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:29.82,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Monet says that we should take appropriate caution when dealing with the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:34.51,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,That's why I chose to send the duo after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:38.05,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The two who {\i1}never{\i0} miss their mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.14,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The hit men of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:49.57,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,The Yeti Cool Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.57,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Only six left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:58.26,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I thought they'd give us more trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.41,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,but it's probably best if we finish it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.85,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Just like these three...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.76,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Coolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.67,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,It's me.  Right off the top,\Nwe took care of three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.35,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Pirate Hunter Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.27,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,The Cat Burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.20,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,The Soul King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:46.24,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,You'll find the corpses\Nat the bottom of a cliff in zone F-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.85,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,We'll leave the disposal to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.81,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,You killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.28,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Isn't that why we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:53.03,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,Well... I guess it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:57.20,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,If you don't want people to die, {\i1}then don't call us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.73,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!  Master said either way was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:03.85,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.  Don't get hot under the collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.60,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Woops, I slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.06,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Let's go, coolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.99,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,Please continue with the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.92,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,540)}Caesar Clown's Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:22.76,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?  They're already dead, Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.73,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.84,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:31.29,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,The Straw Hat Pirates are members of\Nthe Worst Generation, the same as Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:34.76,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,The government is keeping just as close an eye\Non them as they are on Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:39.53,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,The newspapers made grand claims\Nthat they had completely recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.38,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,so I thought they'd be more impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:43.45,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.42,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,You know them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:52.03,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Two years ago at Sabaody, and again at Marineford...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:55.75,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,You've gotten involved with Straw Hat twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.00,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.29,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Does this mean that you called them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.88,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Didn't I already tell you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:13.67,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Until we crossed paths at the entrance,\NI had no idea that you'd locked them in the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.93,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If I had known, I would have warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.45,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down\Njust because you've locked them in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:28.88,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Because of your naivety,\NI wasn't able to bluff the Navy into going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:33.40,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I don't want what's going on here to leak out\Nany more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.18,Flashbacks,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.37,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,I'm doing an experiment.  Call later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.25,Flashbacks,Gasmask,0,0,0,,But a Warlord's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.86,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.69,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,You're going to stay on Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.35,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,It took a lot of effort for me to get to this island\Nsince it can't be reached with a Log.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.05,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,I did it because there was\Na hidden Government facility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.18,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,What's your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:19:00.04,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Since Dr. Vegapunk formerly used this lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:03.24,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,there should still be evidence\Nof what the World Government is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:08.24,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,That is to say, projects that they're working on today\Nshould have started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:14.00,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Anyway, as long as I'm free to walk around\Nthe island and laboratory, that'll be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.79,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,I can help you out around here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:24.73,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Neither of us has to get involved in the other's business.  Of course, don't tell anyone that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.59,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Not even Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:34.22,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,You seem very well informed!  How do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:38.99,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Would you prefer it if I was an ignorant fool that didn't know what he was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.65,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,Well now, aren't we two birds of a feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.79,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,We can't trust each other,\Nbut your proposition seems harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.37,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,Right, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.33,Flashbacks,Monet,0,0,0,,From North Blue, the Surgeon of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:59.76,Flashbacks,Monet,0,0,0,,You have the Ope Ope Fruit ability.  I see that you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:06.58,Flashbacks,Monet,0,0,0,,On this island, there are many ex-convicts\Nwho lost the use of their legs to the poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.09,Flashbacks,Monet,0,0,0,,Can you help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:18.47,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Well, if you'd actually called for help,\NI imagine you'd have been more clever about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:23.92,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,You went through all of the effort of ingratiating yourself to the Government and becoming a Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:28.03,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,so I suppose you wouldn't try to expose this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.87,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:30.78,Main,Law,0,0,0,,A moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:36.54,Main,Law,0,0,0,,you said that if you left the kids from\Nthe Biscuits Room alone, they'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.15,Main,Law,0,0,0,,What did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:44.21,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Every day I give them a drug-laced candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:48.15,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It's sweet and fizzy to the taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:50.82,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,and releases an intoxicating gas into the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.80,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,They're all addicted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:57.84,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,I can't have them going back home, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:02.39,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You're twisted, alright.\NReminds me of a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:08.89,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to join the battle with the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.71,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If you need me, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.49,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'll cut the head off of anyone you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.44,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,It's hard to handle people who are so sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,There it is again!  What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:27.01,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This isn't an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.15,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Are we under attack?  It's an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.44,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Was that an explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.00,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It's in the direction we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Could it have something to do\Nwith whoever made this footprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.62,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's something out there, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They feel like monsters.  Two of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's go back!  Nami and Chopper are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.53,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:07.01,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Oh no!  If this place collapses, the children will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:10.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy!  Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:13.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They'll never make it in time!\NThe two of us have to deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.44,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Can you see them, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.55,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,How many enemies are there?  What are they like?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:30.23,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:36.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,nobody out here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.31,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.35,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.24,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Oh, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.50,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,It's getting noisy out there.\NIs somebody here to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:52.25,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Law?  Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.39,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,No, this is the snow mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:55.85,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,so it's got to be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:01.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hey, Brownie!  You know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Who's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:04.71,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You'd better answer, or else I'll do {\i1}this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:06.97,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.36,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Beam!  {\alpha&HFF&}Beam!  Beam!  Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.74,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Beam!  Beam!  {\alpha&HFF&}Beam!  Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:11.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Beam!  Beam!  Beam!  {\alpha&HFF&}Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:12.80,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Beam!  Beam!  Beam!  Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:15.32,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're disrespecting the beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.15,0:23:20.95,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Searching for them is pointless. They never show themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:23.30,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Even we don't know what their faces look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:30.09,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,But once you hire them\Nand give them their money, they always get the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:36.92,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,All we know about them is that their feet are huge,\Nbut their voices are quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:44.56,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Oh, and another thing we know is that\Nthey are giant beast-men covered in fur!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:50.02,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They're the hit man duo\Nwho appear in blizzards on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:54.87,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we also know their names, Rock and Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.90,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,People call them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:58.50,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,the Yeti Cool Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.69,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They were born in an undisclosed snowy country,\Nand their ages are{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:03.91,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You know {\i1}loads{\i0} of stuff about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.62,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,But nobody knows what they look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.58,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They're both gigantic and powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.18,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,They've come to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:15.26,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,You're already on their hit list.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:22.00,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Brownbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.00,0:24:26.52,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You're on the hit list as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:31.07,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:34.05,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,He's huge, but I didn't hear him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.05,0:24:36.22,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Wha?!  Are you Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:37.37,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,I'm Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:38.93,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I thought you said something ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:41.88,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I must have misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.88,0:24:44.43,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I nearly had a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.43,0:24:47.45,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Master must have contracted you to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:51.52,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,So hurry up and free me from these chains,\Nthen kill the Straw Hat{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.95,0:24:56.35,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You didn't mishear me.  Master put a hit on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.35,0:24:58.29,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.29,0:24:59.99,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:04.28,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Oh, and that guy... What was his name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:05.46,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:07.22,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,He went and got himself captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.22,0:25:11.30,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,That stupid hairy-faced man...\NHe was famous for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:13.62,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Ohhh right, Brownbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.62,0:25:14.89,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Eh, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.69,0:25:16.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.46,0:25:20.98,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,He's an idiot so he's easy to use,\Nbut he has become a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.98,0:25:22.11,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,We don't need him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.82,0:25:23.96,Main,Caesar,0,0,0,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:32.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey, look!  There's smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.98,0:25:38.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami!  Chopper!  Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:41.50,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,You're Brownbeard, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.50,0:25:44.13,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,You did well to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.13,0:25:47.24,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,You're all better now.  You can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:48.46,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.89,0:25:52.97,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Master!  Today was quiet, as normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.97,0:25:57.71,Flashbacks,Caesar,0,0,0,,I see.  Brownbeard, you are a most reliable guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.88,0:26:01.10,Flashbacks,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.35,0:26:05.76,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.91,0:26:09.27,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.06,0:26:15.98,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:19.69,Main,Brownbeard,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.13,0:26:27.86,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Don't be so hot-headed.  Die coolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.16,0:26:39.19,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Hey Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.69,0:26:41.21,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.21,0:26:44.84,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Quit shooting.\NYou'll bring this place down and kill the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.84,0:26:48.26,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Oh.  That wouldn't be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.91,0:26:51.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.18,0:26:52.94,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,How terrible!  Their own ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.42,0:26:56.77,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Look there, the captain has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.53,0:26:59.33,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Taking them out comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.15,0:27:07.71,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's that?  They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.71,0:27:08.79,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.79,0:27:10.66,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,No, they look a little bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.66,0:27:14.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You better not have hurt my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.77,0:27:29.35,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Wha... He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.97,0:27:46.52,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.52,0:27:47.12,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.01,0:27:51.29,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sorry!  They got Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.27,0:28:03.86,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,This is the only one\Nthat we're supposed to capture alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.86,0:28:06.46,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,A robot with Vegapunk's laser, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.72,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Now we can kill everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.72,0:28:12.93,Main,Rock,0,0,0,,Okay.  Let's enjoy the hunt as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.93,0:28:14.62,Main,Scotch,0,0,0,,Coolly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.55,0:28:22.42,captions_soft,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,700)\pos(640,540)}Laboratory - Backdoor
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.46,0:28:28.74,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.74,0:28:30.10,Main,Gasmask2,0,0,0,,Law-san, where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:36.19,Main,Gasmask,0,0,0,,We just ran into the Navy not too far from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:02.73,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.80,0:29:09.20,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Where I go... is my business.
